(c) any judgment registered in the High Court under the British and Colonial Judgments Act, Chapter 16 of the 1959 Edition of the Laws, before the commencement of the order, had been registered in the High Court under this Part, and anything done in relation thereto under the British and Colonial Judgments Act, Chapter 16 of the 1959 Edition of the Laws, or any rules of court or other provisions applicable to the said Act, had been done under this Part or the corresponding rules of court or other provisions applicable to this Part.
